1
00:00:01,980 --> 00:00:05,900
Tak kusangka hidupku
akan jadi seperti ini.

2
00:00:06,550 --> 00:00:09,190
Tinggal di apartemen jelek
yang dindingnya tipis.

3
00:00:09,570 --> 00:00:12,700
Diperlakukan seperti orang bodoh oleh manajer
muda di tempat kerja sambilanku.

4
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:16,210
Diremehkan oleh bocah,
dan meminta maaf padanya.

5
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:20,380
Cuma punya satu pacar seumur hidup.
Itu pun semasa SMP.

6
00:00:20,690 --> 00:00:23,290
Salah sejak dari manakah aku ini?

7
00:00:25,970 --> 00:00:26,890
Eh?

8
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:29,840
Tak mungkin!

9
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,060
Siapa preman norak ini?!

10
00:00:39,270 --> 00:00:43,610
Ini aku! Aku saat SMP!
Noraknya kebangetan!

11
00:00:44,030 --> 00:00:45,440
Lapar, ya.

12
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:47,430
Pengin makan katsudon.

13
00:00:51,140 --> 00:00:52,840
Ada apa, Takemichi?

14
00:00:53,660 --> 00:00:56,000
Maaf.
Aku harus pergi.

15
00:00:56,190 --> 00:00:58,130
Eh? Ke mana?

16
00:01:02,090 --> 00:01:02,930
Iya.

17
00:01:03,870 --> 00:01:05,570
Loh, Hanagaki?

18
00:01:06,170 --> 00:01:07,550
Kamu berantem lagi?

19
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:10,590
Enggak baik kalau sering berantem, loh.

20
00:01:16,180 --> 00:01:17,500
Loh?

21
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:22,570
Jangan-jangan, kamu temannya kakakku?

22
00:01:23,010 --> 00:01:24,600
Tachibana Naoto.

23
00:01:24,930 --> 00:01:25,830
Oh, iya.

24
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:28,480
12 tahun lagi,
dia juga akan mati.

25
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:31,510
Pada 1 Juli, 12 tahun dari sekarang.

26
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,600
Kakakmu akan ...

27
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:34,620
... mati!

28
00:01:36,050 --> 00:01:39,170
Lalu, saat itu, kau juga akan mati bersamanya.

29
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:42,940
Tanggal 1 Juli 2017!

30
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,220
Ingatlah hari ini, Naoto!

31
00:01:45,470 --> 00:01:47,700
Lalu, lindungilah Kakakmu!

32
00:01:48,170 --> 00:01:48,960
Ya.

33
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:50,789
Aku paham!

34
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,820
Bekerjasamalah denganku!

35
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:59,270
Kau pasti bisa ...

36
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,180
... menyelamatkan kakakku!

37
00:02:02,110 --> 00:02:03,530
Aku ...

38
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:06,290
... menyelamatkan Tachibana?

39
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:21,579
Melintasi waktu.

40
00:02:21,579 --> 00:02:22,240
Hah?

41
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:26,520
Aku punya asumsi tersendiri
mengenai kekuatanmu ini.

42
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:31,840
Kau bisa kembali dari hari ini,
tanggal 4 Juli 2017 ...

43
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:34,760
... menuju tanggal 4 Juli 2005.

44
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:38,700
Artinya, kau bisa kembali ke hari
yang sama pada 12 tahun lalu.

45
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:42,000
Kurasa itulah kekuatan
yang dimiliki olehmu.

46
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,000
Wah ....

47
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:50,880
Kerah kami ditarik, dan diberi bogem mentah

48
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:55,740
sehingga kami sempoyongan,
lalu jongkok bersebelahan

49
00:02:55,840 --> 00:03:00,520
Di tengah hujan yang diprediksi,
kau menyeringai

50
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:06,330
lalu berbohong bahwa "luka pasti akan sembuh"

51
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:09,690
Bahkan adu mulut yang sering dilakukan

52
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:14,460
tak bisa kulakukan dengan baik

53
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:19,710
Jangan katakan candaan
yang membosankan

54
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:25,030
Rasa bosannya pun tampak jelas di mataku!

55
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:32,620
Tak peduli walau seberapa banyak air
mata yang mengaliri pipi lebamku ini

56
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:39,170
melalui hati yang goyah
bersanding dengan bahu

57
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:43,820
kau pasti bisa menghindari
akhir buruk yang menghantui!

58
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:49,370
Kenapa rasa sakit ini lebih
nyaman dibanding kebahagiaan?

59
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:53,790
Bahkan rasa sakit ini kian menggema!

60
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:58,430
Sambil menggigit lidah dan
mengenakan baju basah,

61
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,720
mari kita tertawakan wajah sembap ini

62
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:06,770
Lalu di tengah malam bermandikan hujan

63
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:13,870
kita ikrarkan balas dendam!

64
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:21,700
(#2 Menentang)

65
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,339
'Ngantuk!

66
00:04:19,350 --> 00:04:21,200
Itu bagian penting.

67
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:22,990
Eh? Oke ....

68
00:04:23,010 --> 00:04:25,130
Lalu, yang itu.
Sudah dibaca dengan saksama?

69
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:26,370
Ah, iya.

70
00:04:26,970 --> 00:04:28,250
Lalu, yang berikutnya.

71
00:04:29,890 --> 00:04:31,080
Itu berlebihan.

72
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:33,950
Nah, yang itu.
Ingatlah juga bagian itu.

73
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:36,290
Dua hari berlalu sejak saat itu,

74
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:40,520
aku dikurung di kamar Naoto,
dan nyaris enggak tidur.

75
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:48,190
Berkaitan dengan Geng Tokyo Manji,
kuingin kau mengingatnya.

76
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,290
Naoto enggak main-main!

77
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,360
Dia berniat membunuhku!

78
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:58,409
5 hari lalu, pada tanggal 1 Juli,

79
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:03,500
Tachibana terlibat perseteruan dengan
organisasi kriminal Geng Tokyo Manji,

80
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,900
lalu meninggal.

81
00:05:05,810 --> 00:05:10,770
Saat festival, dia berada di kedai
yang ditabrak oleh truk.

82
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:13,280
Usianya 26 tahun.

83
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:20,100
Dalam laporan tersebut, terdapat perbuatan
Geng Tokyo Manji yang tak dipublikasi.

84
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:24,290
Pendahuluku melakukan
penyelidikan yang mengancam nyawa.

85
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:28,480
Foto terakhir itu adalah dirinya sendiri.

86
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,260
Eh?

87
00:05:29,450 --> 00:05:32,880
Dia dibunuh karena identitasnya
ketahuan saat penyelidikan.

88
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:36,040
Di rongga mata jenazahnya ....

89
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,830
Alih-alih terdapat bola mata,

90
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:43,070
justru di sana terdapat media yang berisi
video seluruh proses pembunuhannya.

91
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:46,340
Setelah terus mengajukan perubahan jabatan ...

92
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:50,230
... setengah tahun lalu,
aku menjadi penerusnya.

93
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:55,170
Walau separuh alasannya karena
ingin menghindari kemarahan publik,

94
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,480
tetapi kematian penyelidik itu disembunyikan.

95
00:05:57,730 --> 00:06:01,390
Sebelum itu, Geng Tokyo Manji
berada dalam kendali Kisaki Tetta ....

96
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:08,120
Naoto berusaha menyampaikan padaku berbagai
informasi tentang Geng Tokyo Manji.

97
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:13,600
Tapi, apa ini diperlukan
untuk menyelamatkan Tachibana?

98
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,930
Kalau membahas tentang
kelemahan dari kekuatanmu,

99
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,880
yakni kau hanya bisa kembali
ke hari ini di 12 tahun lalu.

100
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:22,340
Itu cuma asumsimu saja, 'kan?

101
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,110
Karena kau saat ini masih hidup,

102
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:28,360
maka bisa dipastikan kejadian itu nyata,

103
00:06:28,690 --> 00:06:30,690
tapi aku tak yakin bisa
kembali lagi ke masa lalu ....

104
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,690
Kembali ke hari meninggalnya Kakakku!

105
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:35,940
Jika kita mencegahnya
pergi ke festival,

106
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:38,470
mungkin Kakakku bisa terselamatkan.

107
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:42,500
Tapi, karena tak bisa
kembali ke waktu spesifik,

108
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,920
maka kita harus lakukan apa saja
yang kita bisa saat ini!

109
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:50,000
Bergegaslah melintasi waktu,
kembali ke masa SMP di 12 tahun lalu,

110
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:51,780
dan temuilah orang tertentu.

111
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,820
Orang tertentu?

112
00:06:54,409 --> 00:06:55,880
Dua pemimpin Touman,

113
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,880
Sano Manjirou,

114
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,250
dan Kisaki Tetta.

115
00:06:59,409 --> 00:07:00,400
Ngeri!

116
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:04,540
Sano dan Kisaki.
Andai mereka tak bertemu,

117
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:07,230
Geng Tokyo Manji yang
saat ini takkan pernah ada.

118
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:08,000
Hah?

119
00:07:08,370 --> 00:07:12,360
Sehingga, Kakakku takkan terlibat
perseteruan yang membuatnya mati.

120
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:13,740
Rupanya begitu.

121
00:07:14,050 --> 00:07:18,430
Jika aku kembali lagi ke masa SMP,
dan mencegah mereka bertemu ....

122
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,210
Aku paham, sih.

123
00:07:21,350 --> 00:07:23,280
Tapi 'gimana caranya
aku balik lagi ke masa lalu?

124
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:27,990
Takemichi. Katamu, kau menjabat tanganku
saat dirimu berada di masa lalu, ya?

125
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,620
Ah, iya.

126
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:32,320
Mungkin itu pemicunya.

127
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:36,159
Berjabat tangan, ya?

128
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:39,950
Saat itu, aku terselamatkan olehmu.

129
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:45,280
Karena hal itu, mungkin aku jadi
"bagian" dari kekuatanmu.

130
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:47,390
Oh, begitu.

131
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:49,690
Walau mungkin pikirnya aku ini orang gila,

132
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:52,890
tapi karena dia percaya bahwa
kubisa melintasi waktu,

133
00:07:53,050 --> 00:07:54,730
maka dia bisa serius sejauh ini.

134
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:58,290
Takemichi.
Sudah siap?

135
00:07:58,630 --> 00:08:01,800
Bahkan aku pun,
tak mau kalah dari Naoto ...

136
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:02,860
Ya!

137
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,240
... soal perasaan ingin
menyelamatkan Tachibana!

138
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:10,130
Sano dan Kisaki. Mereka bertemu
12 tahun lalu pada bulan Agustus.

139
00:08:10,570 --> 00:08:13,570
Dekatilah salah satu dari mereka,
lalu ikuti tindakannya,

140
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,520
dan cegah pertemuan itu terjadi.

141
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,330
Ya, akan coba kulakukan!

142
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,990
Hanya kau yang bisa ...

143
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:25,240
... menyelamatkan Kakakku!

144
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:38,330
Oke!

145
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:38,789
Hah?

146
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,860
Ayo mulai!

147
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:44,370
Loh? Naoto mana?

148
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:49,000
Jangan banyak basa-basi, goblok!

149
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:51,080
- Buruan hajar!
- Bunuh!

150
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,890
Tunggu dulu!

151
00:08:51,930 --> 00:08:54,040
Apa kau belum makan, berengsek?!

152
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:56,060
Jangan tidur, goblok!

153
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,100
- Ayo hajar!
- Hah?

154
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:02,680
Hanagaki!
Aku bertaruh 1.000 yen padamu!

155
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:04,190
Eh?!

156
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:06,050
Situasi macam apa ini?!

157
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:07,650
Tunggu dulu!

158
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,770
Hari ini 12 tahun lalu!

159
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,810
Sesuai perkataan Naoto!

160
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,260
Tunggu! Oi!

161
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:20,690
Aku benar-benar kembali
melintasi waktu.

162
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:22,380
Ah!

163
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:25,940
Woi, Hanagaki sudah bangun, tuh.

164
00:09:26,590 --> 00:09:29,090
Aku pingsan, ya?

165
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:32,750
Goblok! Jangan tepar cuma
karena kena bogem sekali!

166
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,620
Mereka taruhan pakai uang!

167
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:37,390
Jangan tunjukkan duel
yang membosankan.

168
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,810
Duel?

169
00:09:38,970 --> 00:09:40,980
Iya, 'kan, Kiyomasa?

170
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:50,840
Luka di alis itu merupakan
tanda pentolan SMP Shibuya!

171
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,960
Namanya adalah Kiyomizu Masataka!

172
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:59,150
Kalau enggak bisa mengumpulkan penonton,
judi sabung orangnya berakhir.

173
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:01,280
Judi sabung orang?

174
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:05,390
Oh, iya. Tadi itu sabung
yang mempertaruhkan uang.

175
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:06,850
Aku mulai ingat!

176
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:09,740
Mereka itu bandar judi!

177
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:14,070
Untuk saat ini, taburlah garam di atas lukanya.

178
00:10:15,090 --> 00:10:16,090
Rasakan!

179
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:18,610
Jangan meringkuk kayak kura-kura!

180
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:19,900
Diri, woi!

181
00:10:19,930 --> 00:10:22,190
Biar kuperbaiki nyalimu itu!

182
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,170
Oh, iya!

183
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:25,580
Aku budaknya mereka!

184
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,770
Yang harus patuh pada mereka!

185
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:29,470
Kura-kura ini kenapa, dah?

186
00:10:29,650 --> 00:10:31,900
Red, sisakan jatahku untuk menyiksanya.

187
00:10:33,690 --> 00:10:35,680
Kau memang payah, ya!

188
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:44,870
Aku dipaksa melawan
orang yang tak kukenal.

189
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:47,180
Kalau kalah, bakal dihajar habis-habisan.

190
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:49,590
Setiap harinya.

191
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:51,850
Aku bagai hidup di neraka.

192
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,620
Karenanya, aku kabur.

193
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,090
Sa ... kit!

194
00:10:58,530 --> 00:11:02,180
Aku mencampakkan temanku,
serta pacarku Tachibana.

195
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:07,770
Tachibana!

196
00:11:08,250 --> 00:11:10,120
Lain kali yang serius, lah.

197
00:11:10,330 --> 00:11:11,780
Aku bosan banget hari ini.

198
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,770
Ayo pulang.

199
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:15,340
Makan ramen, yuk.

200
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:16,700
- Anu.
- Hah?

201
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:20,570
Walah, kau kuat juga, ya.
Masih sadar?

202
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:22,480
Eng ....

203
00:11:23,610 --> 00:11:25,400
Bang Kiyomasa dan kawan-kawan ...

204
00:11:25,530 --> 00:11:27,330
... itu dari Geng Tokyo Manji, 'kan?

205
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:30,080
Aku ingin bertemu dengan
pemimpin Geng Tokyo Manji,

206
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,080
baik itu Sano maupun Kisaki.

207
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:35,500
Apa tak bisa diusahakan, ya ....

208
00:11:37,460 --> 00:11:39,800
Tak masalah juga sih kalau
memang enggak bisa.

209
00:11:46,470 --> 00:11:48,270
Bawakan pemukul!

210
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:04,160
Maafkan ....

211
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,550
Oi.

212
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:15,470
Kayaknya harus segera kita hentikan.

213
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:16,940
I-Iya.

214
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:19,770
Kiyomasa, gawat!
Nanti dia bisa mati!

215
00:12:28,110 --> 00:12:30,690
Oi bangunlah, Hanagaki!

216
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:41,060
Kalau nantinya nama "Sano"
keluar dari mulutmu lagi,

217
00:12:41,930 --> 00:12:43,450
kau paham risikonya, 'kan?

218
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:44,800
Kau akan kubunuh!

219
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:48,800
Ngeri!

220
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:51,880
Dia itu kenapa, sih?
Enggak bisa diajak ngobrol sama sekali!

221
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,970
Kalau begini, mustahil bertemu mereka!

222
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:57,150
Kalau kusebut namanya,
aku betulan akan dibunuh!

223
00:12:57,330 --> 00:12:59,960
Apa dia benar-benar anak SMP?!

224
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:17,120
Bertemu dengan pemimpin Geng Tokyo Manji?

225
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,990
Budak sepertiku bisa melakukannya?

226
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,250
Mustahil!

227
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:23,080
Ini mustahil, Naoto!

228
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,480
Aku lupa.

229
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,960
Aku benar-benar lupa.

230
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,280
Wah, gila!

231
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,760
Aku tetaplah aku.

232
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:37,060
Walaupun di kehidupan kedua,
yang payah tetaplah payah.

233
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:40,420
Aku mau kembali.

234
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,500
Kembali ke masa depan.

235
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:47,210
'Gimana caranya supaya aku bisa kembali?

236
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:49,740
Oh, iya.

237
00:13:51,190 --> 00:13:53,010
Jabat tangan itu pemicunya!

238
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:56,370
Jika bertemu Naoto ....

239
00:14:03,730 --> 00:14:04,550
Loh?

240
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,750
Apa dia enggak di rumah?

241
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,150
Pasti karena Naoto!

242
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,180
Asal aku berjabat tangan dengannya ...

243
00:14:10,330 --> 00:14:11,600
... aku bisa kembali ke masa depan!

244
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:13,910
Hanya kau yang bisa ...

245
00:14:14,410 --> 00:14:15,820
... menyelamatkan Kakakku!

246
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:20,650
Apa aku akan melarikan diri lagi?

247
00:14:23,390 --> 00:14:25,420
Loh, Hanagaki?

248
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:27,210
Tachibana?!

249
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,280
Kenapa?

250
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,400
Kok malah tanya.

251
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,220
Di situ kan rumahnya Hina.

252
00:14:35,090 --> 00:14:36,110
Oh, iya.

253
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,510
Tentu saja, ya.

254
00:14:37,530 --> 00:14:38,970
Kamu berantem lagi?

255
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,580
Maaf.

256
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,430
Hari ini lukamu cukup parah.

257
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:44,700
Kamu baik-baik saja?

258
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:46,140
Ah, iya.

259
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,730
Sama sekali enggak masalah!

260
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:53,660
Duh. Kenapa cowok itu
sering banget berantem?

261
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:56,930
Andai saja Hina juga cowok.

262
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:58,080
Eh?

263
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:02,170
Lalu,

264
00:15:03,370 --> 00:15:06,320
Hina-lah yang akan
melindungi Hanagaki!

265
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:11,800
Karena Hina ikut karate,
pasti kuat kalau jadi cowok!

266
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:18,140
Lalu,

267
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:21,010
aku juga akan melindungimu, Hina!

268
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:25,170
Aku memanggilnya Hina.

269
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:26,160
Ya!

270
00:15:26,930 --> 00:15:28,880
Ah, aku terbawa suasana!

271
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:31,180
Aku lebih suka panggilan itu!

272
00:15:38,860 --> 00:15:41,450
Tapi, Hina-lah yang jadi pelindung.

273
00:15:41,610 --> 00:15:42,240
Hah?

274
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:46,240
Soalnya, Takemichi itu cengeng, sih.

275
00:15:48,130 --> 00:15:51,020
Kalau jadi cowok, pasti Hina-lah
yang jauh lebih kuat!

276
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:54,430
Oi, oi! Enggak 'gitu juga!

277
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,500
Aku cuma 'nangis waktu itu doang, 'kan?!

278
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,090
Apa iya?

279
00:15:58,110 --> 00:15:59,330
Lupakan, dong!

280
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:01,020
Ogah.
Enggak bakal kulupakan!

281
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:10,530
Dadah!

282
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:12,150
Sampai besok, ya!

283
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:13,040
Iya!

284
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,480
Aku pulang!

285
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:47,390
12 tahun mendatang.

286
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:50,420
Aku tak pacaran dengannya lagi.

287
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:53,190
Aku pun tak menemuinya
bertahun-tahun.

288
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:58,860
Aku tak memiliki kewajiban menyelamatkannya.

289
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:02,920
Hina akan melindungi Hanagaki!

290
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,960
Tapi, dia ....

291
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:11,050
Dia tak boleh mati!

292
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:18,109
Takemichi!

293
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:20,490
Takuya?

294
00:17:20,670 --> 00:17:22,940
Kenapa kau bisa kalah darinya?

295
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,780
Ini bukan kau yang biasanya!

296
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,420
Eh? Oh ....

297
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:28,220
Soal kemarin, ya?

298
00:17:28,670 --> 00:17:29,570
Maaf.

299
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:30,610
Oi.

300
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:34,170
Bisa bicara sebentar?

301
00:17:36,610 --> 00:17:38,060
Mereka bakal melakukannya lagi.

302
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:39,740
Judi sabung orang.

303
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:42,760
Belakangan ini jadi tiap hari, ya.

304
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,510
Petarung hari ini ...

305
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:46,130
... katanya Takuya.

306
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:48,040
- Eh?!
- Hah?!

307
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:48,880
Aduh!

308
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,650
Yamamoto Takuya.

309
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:53,950
Dia tubuhnya lemah.

310
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:57,290
Kalau tak salah, saat itu dia sampai sekarat.

311
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,380
Mustahil bagi Takuya!

312
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,270
Dia enggak jago berantem!

313
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:03,230
Cobalah bilang begitu sama Kiyomasa.

314
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:06,030
Memangnya kalian bisa?!

315
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,100
Bahkan jika posisinya bisa digantikan,

316
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:10,610
aku ingin menggantikannya!

317
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:12,170
Akkun.

318
00:18:12,290 --> 00:18:14,460
Dia ingin menggantikan Takuya, ya.

319
00:18:14,690 --> 00:18:17,440
Mereka takkan mendengar omongan orang lain.

320
00:18:20,430 --> 00:18:21,610
Akkun.

321
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,020
Terima kasih, Akkun.

322
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,020
Aku tak melakukan apa-apa!

323
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:29,040
Takemichi.

324
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:29,700
Eh?

325
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,480
Lihatlah!

326
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:35,340
Dendammu akan kubalaskan!

327
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:39,000
Kalau menang, traktir aku gyudon, ya!

328
00:18:40,130 --> 00:18:41,260
Takuya!

329
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:43,580
Sialan!

330
00:18:44,250 --> 00:18:45,530
Pokoknya, ya.

331
00:18:45,890 --> 00:18:48,060
Perasaanmu jangan sampai kalah, Takuya!

332
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:48,700
Iya.

333
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:49,700
Aku paham.

334
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:51,180
Berjuanglah, Takuya!

335
00:18:51,320 --> 00:18:52,900
Cuci tanganmu dulu, Yamagishi!

336
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:53,630
Ah.

337
00:18:54,890 --> 00:18:57,720
Nyaris kusentuh dengan tangan kotor.

338
00:19:03,050 --> 00:19:04,960
Walau kukira mereka norak,

339
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:07,070
tetapi mereka sangatlah keren!

340
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:09,630
Ternyata pada saat SMP,

341
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:12,460
aku punya teman-teman sebaik ini, ya?

342
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:14,610
Oke, ayo mulai!

343
00:19:14,690 --> 00:19:15,130
Yoi!

344
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:16,960
Kalau terlalu serius,
nanti bakalan kentut!

345
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:18,350
Cuma kau yang begitu.

346
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:20,430
Takemichi, ayo buruan!

347
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:21,870
Iya!

348
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,430
Jangan bercanda!

349
00:19:28,770 --> 00:19:30,110
Oi!

350
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:32,390
Para hadirin yang telah berkumpul!

351
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:36,240
Petarung hari ini sesuai
yang tertera di surel!

352
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:38,210
Kojima dari SMP Sakura!

353
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,350
Hei!

354
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:41,190
Jangan bilang hei, goblok!

355
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,960
Jangan belagu, botak!

356
00:19:42,970 --> 00:19:45,150
Kalau kalah, kutinju kau sebelum balik!

357
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:48,110
Lalu, ada Yamamoto dari SMP Mizo!

358
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:49,550
Mati sana, pirang!

359
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,160
Jangan takut, bangsat!

360
00:19:51,310 --> 00:19:54,080
Peluang menangnya 4 banding 6,
Kojima agak diuntungkan!

361
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:56,230
Tunjukkan nyalimu, Yamada!

362
00:19:56,330 --> 00:19:57,440
Bukannya Yamamoto?

363
00:19:57,610 --> 00:19:59,320
Beda 'dikit mah enggak masalah!

364
00:19:59,410 --> 00:20:01,170
Aku bertaruh 500 yen padamu!

365
00:20:01,190 --> 00:20:03,060
Kalau kau kalah, aku bakal bokek!

366
00:20:19,570 --> 00:20:20,580
Oke, maju sini.

367
00:20:20,650 --> 00:20:22,490
Akan kubelah kau jadi 3 bagian!

368
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:32,350
Mulailah.

369
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:36,830
Tunggu dulu!!!

370
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,250
Hah?

371
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:46,120
Ta-Takemichi?!

372
00:20:46,570 --> 00:20:48,190
Apa-apaan kau, sialan?

373
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:49,240
Siapa bocah ini?

374
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:51,440
Bocah kelas 2 jangan sok keras!

375
00:20:51,610 --> 00:20:52,910
Hah, kelas 2?

376
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:57,030
Yah.

377
00:20:57,450 --> 00:21:00,910
Bukannya kalau menonton duel
yang sama terus-terusan bakal membosankan?

378
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:03,660
Kalian pasti ingin menonton
yang lebih seru, 'kan?

379
00:21:03,730 --> 00:21:05,880
Lah, bukannya kau yang
tepar setelah kena bogem sekali?

380
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,160
Jangan ikut campur, goblok!

381
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:10,380
Yang lebih seru?

382
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,830
Aku harus menghadapinya ....

383
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,700
Co-Contohnya, nih.

384
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:18,310
Aku tak boleh lari!

385
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:20,510
Kau ini kenapa?!

386
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,140
Jangan ganggu!

387
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:23,040
O-Oi.

388
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,550
Takemichi?!

389
00:21:26,620 --> 00:21:28,090
Raja melawan ...

390
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:29,250
... budak.

391
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:30,470
Oi, oi, oi!

392
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:31,960
Orang sableng muncul!

393
00:21:31,980 --> 00:21:33,850
Dia ngelantur apaan, sih?

394
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,460
Hah?

395
00:21:34,530 --> 00:21:36,140
Apa maksudmu?!

396
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:37,820
Takemichi?

397
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,690
Jangan-jangan!

398
00:21:40,290 --> 00:21:41,750
Kak Kiyomasa.

399
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:55,330
Ayo gelut satu lawan satu!

400
00:22:00,230 --> 00:22:02,120
Baik di masa lalu,
maupun masa mendatang,

401
00:22:02,730 --> 00:22:05,630
kalau aku tetap sama,
maka takkan ada perubahan.

402
00:22:05,810 --> 00:22:06,580
Hah?

403
00:22:07,110 --> 00:22:09,640
Aku ... takkan lari lagi!

404
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,700
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

405
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

406
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

407
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita berciuman di tengah dinginnya malam

408
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

409
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

410
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

411
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

412
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

413
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

414
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

415
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

416
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

417
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

418
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

419
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

420
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


